name: Lucidroid
desc:
An android that looks like Lucid. It allows you access to General Store functions via the #cVisit Shop# button in its equipment window. Must have an #cAndroid Heart# equipped to operate.
The android rank must be the same or higher than the rank of the Android Heart.
